OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting is to
OL,8,Fvisit a meningitis vaccination centre
OL,9,Fin Kent on Thursday after a deadly
OL,10,Foutbreak of the infection.
OL,12,FThe University of Kent said 600
OL,13,Fmeningitis B (menB) vaccines had been
OL,14,Fadministered on Wednesday, after
OL,15,Fhundreds of students joined a queue
OL,16,Foutside the campus sports centre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThose who have received the jab will
OL,8,Fneed to return for their second dose
OL,9,Fafter a minimum of four weeks, while
OL,10,F6,500 antibiotics have been given out
OL,11,Fas a precaution, the university said.
OL,13,FAbout 5,000 students from the
OL,14,FCanterbury campus of the University of
OL,15,FKent will be offered the jab,
OL,16,Falongside courses of antibiotics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FIt comes after one school pupil and
OL,8,Fone university student died and 18
OL,9,Fmore cases were being investigated by
OL,10,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,11,Ffollowing an outbreak of meningitis
OL,12,Flinked to a nightclub in Canterbury.
OL,14,FThe UKHSA issued an alert for the NHS
OL,15,Facross England on Wednesday on signs
OL,16,Fand symptoms of meningitis to look out
OL,17,Ffor, though this does not signal the
OL,18,Foutbreak is going to spread nationwide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe alert said the illness being seen
OL,8,Fin the Kent outbreak "has been severe
OL,9,Fwith rapid deterioration" and urges
OL,10,Fclinical staff to take infection
OL,11,Fcontrol measures in the period before
OL,12,Fpatients are put on antibiotics, such
OL,13,Fas face masks and other personal
OL,14,Fprotective equipment (PPE).
OL,16,FIt urges doctors to have a "high index
OL,17,Fof suspicion where a young person aged
OL,18,F16 to 30 attends with consistent signs
OL,19,For symptoms" of the bug.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@YO]xD@\OU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
