OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FStudents from the university halls in
OL,8,FCanterbury who have already left
OL,9,Fcampus will be able to get a menB jab
OL,10,Ffrom their GP, according to the
OL,11,FDepartment of Health.
OL,13,FFive new cases of meningitis were
OL,14,Fannounced by the UKHSA on Wednesday
OL,15,Fmorning, taking the total number being
OL,16,Finvestigated by health officials to 20.
OL,18,FOf these, nine cases have been
OL,19,Fconfirmed in the lab and 11 remain
OL,20,Funder investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FSix of the confirmed cases have been
OL,8,Fconfirmed as the menB strain.
OL,10,FCanterbury Christ Church University,
OL,11,Falso in Kent, confirmed a meningitis
OL,12,Fcase among its students on Wednesday,
OL,13,Fmeaning confirmed or suspected cases
OL,14,Fhave been reported at two universities
OL,15,Fand five schools.
OL,17,FGPs across the country have also been
OL,18,Ftold to prescribe antibiotics to
OL,19,Fanyone who visited Club Chemistry in
OL,20,FCanterbury from March 5-7, plus
OL,21,Fstudents from the University of Kent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThis is to ensure anyone who has left
OL,8,Fcampus can make sure they get the
OL,9,Fright treatment.
OL,11,FThe number of cases is expected to
OL,12,Frise because the incubation period for
OL,13,Fthe infection to when symptoms appear
OL,14,Fis between two and 14 days.
OL,16,FThe UKHSA stressed there are plenty of
OL,17,FNHS stocks of menB vaccines after
OL,18,Fpharmacies reported they were
OL,19,Fstruggling to obtain stock for people
OL,20,Fwho want to pay privately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773885783
OL,3,CHealth Secretary to visit Kent
OL,4,Cvaccination centre after meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FAll reported cases so far have a link
OL,8,Fto Kent, according to the UKHSA.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, French authorities said a
OL,11,Fperson who was admitted to hospital
OL,12,Fwith meningitis in France with links
OL,13,Fto the Kent outbreak is now in a
OL,14,F"stable" condition.
OL,16,FThe French ministry of health told the
OL,17,FPress Association no other cases of
OL,18,Fmeningitis linked to the outbreak in
OL,19,FKent have been reported in France.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
